modName: Black Metal Girl Preset For RaceMenu
summary: A Simple Black Metal Girl Preset For RaceMenu
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=4]So here is a preset for RaceMenu:[/size]

[size=4]A black metal girl[/size]

[size=4]Requirement:
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url](Which mean you also need [url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url])
-[/size][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2812/?]Better Female by Bella 
[/url]-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url][/size][size=4][/size]

[size=3]*Ps: The preset doesn't include the tattoos.
       If you want them, install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50032/?]KJ Tattoos[/url] by Khajiitas.
       These are the tattoos that I used:

       -Kj Arm Paint Full
       -Kj Dragon 4
       -Kj Dragon 2 Back
       -Kj Dragon Side
       -Kj Tribal Arm 2
       -Kj Halo 1[/size]

[size=3]*If you want a more Black Metal looking character, you can change
the eyes to blind(completely white in both eyes)[/size]

*Pss: English isn't my fist language therefore I sincerely apologize for any mistake:)[/center][center][/center]
author: SoullHollow
